Release 30 - dbUnity Release Communication
   Date and Time Saturday 26th October 2019 17:45
Comms Reference  R30 HLD 4.0
   Status Completed
                  Update

Testing is now complete and all streams have signed off the release

Voice Recording only provided a partial sign off, pending further investigation next week into an issue identified in production.

Final Update: Release Closed

We just want to thank all Process SMEs/Testers, who have helped safely release R30 into Production
